            <Label fx:id="noticeField11211" layoutX="605.0" layoutY="567.0" prefHeight="102.0" prefWidth="502.0" text="Library staff are available to assist with finding materials, using equipment, and maintaining a conducive environment. Patrons are expected to follow their instructions and respect their authority in managing the space." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrapText="true">
